#

No-Cook Apple Cranberry Sauce

10 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

CondimentSide Dish

Tags:

No-CookSauceSide Dish

Description

A fresh and vibrant sauce that combines tart cranberries with sweet apples, perfect for topping meats or spreading on bread.

Ingredients

  • fresh cranberries: 2 cups
  • apples (peeled and chopped): 2 medium
  • sugar: 3/4 cup
  • orange juice: 1/2 cup
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
